Interface NodeList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - data type of list
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNodeList, DoubleLinkedList
    public interface NodeList<E>
    NodeList is a custom List interface. It has the the ability of manipulating List with existing nodes. It can use existing nodes to add to list without creating new ones. Or it can remove and return Nodes instead of the data. This way i can use the NodeList's removed nodes for other list.
